text: Charles Dellert (March 26, 1882 - October 28, 1981) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:1981 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Missouri
